gomodel:SYNGO_1317  a     owl:Ontology ;
        rdfs:comment      "Rationale: Figure 3A: Rat hippocampal slices (top and middle) or cultured hippocampal neurons (bottom) were immunostained with anti-RNG105 antibody (green) and costained with anti-RPS6, anti-PSD-95, or anti-staufen antibodies.\n\n25/9/2017 Pim\n- Literal: \"Quantitative analysis revealed that ~88% of the RNG105-localizing granules were associated with ribosomes. Second, some RNG105-localizing granules (~9%) were accumulated near the postsynaptic sites stained with anti-PSD-95 antibody (Fig. 3A), which may be consistent with the previous report that some proportion of polyribosomes is localized near postsynapses\". Experimental description: Rat hippocampal slices or cultured hippocampal neurons" ;
        lego:modelstate   "production" ;
        dc:contributor    "https://orcid.org/0000-0002-1190-4481" , "https://orcid.org/0000-0002-9848-0262" , "https://orcid.org/0000-0002-4419-210X" , "https://orcid.org/0000-0002-2094-7491" ;
        dc:date           "2017-09-25" ;
        dc:title          "SYNGO_CC_1317" ;
        pav:providedBy    "https://syngo.vu.nl" ;
        biolink:in_taxon  "http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/NCBITaxon_10116" .

